## a nicer approach dealing with the stones stone by stone like this
## ${if_match ${execi 30 ${date "+%M" | head -c 1}==0}} ${image ${template1}/00.png -p 134,0 -s 100x188} ${else} ...
## and
## ${if_match ${execi 10 ${date "+%M" | tail -c 2}==0}} ${image ${template1}/00.png -p 270,0 -s 100x188} ${else} ...
## did not work, so here a brute force attempt which might be better 
## anyway, because it doesn't need 16 execi calls, but stays in conky 
## - even though it ifs the living hell of an if construct with 59 elses. 
## But again: that all is internal (at least that).
##########################################################################
